OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fnight in the east with gusty winds to
OL,7,Fstart with but easing through the
OL,8,Fnight. Cloudy in the west with showery
OL,9,Frain clearing northwards. Turning
OL,10,Fmurky around the coasts by dawn and
OL,11,Fleading to a mild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA cloudier start with showery
OL,14,Frain pushing eastwards. Some brighter
OL,15,Fspells developing in the west through
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Lighter winds than of
OL,17,Flate.
